name: Grands!® Cheesy BBQ Cups
author: Pillsbury
summary: Grands!® biscuits make great cups for these barbecue treats!
ingredients: 1 pound lean (at least 80%) ground beef, cooked, drained
1 (10.2 ounce) can Pillsbury® Grands!® Flaky Layers refrigerated biscuits
directions: In 10-inch nonstick skillet, mix cooked beef and barbecue sauce
Heat over medium-high heat, stirring constantly, until hot
Pull each biscuit apart into 2 layers; press each into 4-inch round
Place 1 round in each of 8 greased regular-size muffin cups
Firmly press in bottom and up side, forming 1/4-inch rim
Fill with beef mixture; sprinkle with cheese
Bake at 375 degrees F 13 to 15 minutes or until edges of biscuits are golden brown
